DistrictName: Name defined in your MAP preferences.
District_StateID: District code you have set in MAP preferences.
SchoolName: Name defined in your MAP preferences. If a student has multiple schools, this is the student's School of Record.
School_StateID: State code for the school associated with the student.
StudentID: ID your district provided in the student's MAP profile.
Student_StateID: ID your state uses to identify the student.
ClassName: Class your district provided in the student's MAP profile.
TeacherName: Teacher (Instructor) your district provided in the student's MAP profile.
TeacherID: Describes the satellite campus site of a teacher.
Teacher_StateID: Additional identifier your state uses to identify the teacher.
